---
title: Buffalo Ranch Chicken Sandos with Creamy Slaw
description: When you mix spicy buffalo sauce with cooling ranch dressing, there’s almost no better flavor combination. Tonight, buffalo and ranch are the secret sauces to these mouthwatering chicken sandos. Plus, why just drizzle creamy dressing on your sando when you can have a creamy slaw on the side, too?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/buffalo-ranch-chicken-sandos-3faadea8.jpg
